race.description: Brian Baldwin Tatts Celebration Super Maiden Handicap
race.comment: STUCK IN THE GORGE (1) loomed into it on debut at Scone but just failed to land the winning blow. Is sure to have come on with that run under his belt and is worth following up. IT'S A WRITTEN (8) progressed nicely at the latest, without paying her supporters. Peaking now and is an obvious danger. CRASHMYPLAYA (6) has been knocking on the door for quite some time and gets another good chance to break through. Don't underestimate. RUFUS ATTICUS (10) often leaves himself with too much to do but will prove tough to stop if the pace is genuine. Watch for him bursting through. PRESSIPITATING (9) finds it tough to get off the mark but has runs littered through her from that measure up. Don't dismiss lightly.
